prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor birthday card for Sarah, humorous and lighthearted. In the center, a cartoon illustration of the two people from the reference photo (0937c239-e751-4f1d-bd53-a63bd1dd93b2), highly resembling them. They are standing next to each other, looking slightly overwhelmed and comically buried up to their waists in a giant pile of colorful birthday presents and tangled ribbons. The man on the left has a party hat slightly askew on his head, and the woman on the right is holding a single, unlit birthday candle with a puzzled expression. Their clothing, hairstyles, facial features (including glasses for the woman), and body proportions are exactly the same as in the photo. The background is a soft, celebratory wash of pastel colors with light confetti details. In the safe center area, above the characters, the text "Happy Birthday, Sarah! Hope it's heaps of fun!" is written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The entire design is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
